{"tid":742364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【真係睇唔出】U20田徑賽攞銅牌 呢個跑手報稱16歲","createTime":"2018-07-14T13:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T07:53:37.000Z","uid":29627,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"00586e49aee0b95a48d2014c518388e200a4d40e","tid":742364,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:14:36.000Z","msg":"U20田徑賽攞銅牌 呢個跑手報稱16歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180714/large/1531552940_7101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180714%2Flarge%2F1531552940_7101.jpg&h=a9f1300c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n基比斯希爾報稱只有16歲<br />\n<br />\n埃塞俄比亞一名16歲年輕女跑手，在U20世界田徑錦標賽5000米長跑中勇奪銅牌，但一些網民嘲諷她怎看也不似少於20歲，是超齡參賽。<br />\n<br />\n基比斯希爾(Girmawit Gebrzihair)報稱在2001年11月21日出生，她在芬蘭舉行的U20田徑錦標賽中奪得一面長跑銅牌，但網民紛紛質疑她的年歲。一名網民說：「16歲？這女子經歷過美國南北戰爭、兩次世界大戰，又看著球王比利領導的巴西隊奪得1970年的世界盃。」另一人說：「除了查看護照外，難道沒有其他方法控制此類事情發生？實在令人難以置信。」<br />\n<br />\n質疑基比斯希爾年齡的人當中，包括西班牙短跑好手胡斯爾路斯(Oscar Husillos)。他在Twitter上載基比斯希爾的照片，並尖酸刻薄地寫著：「她的子女和孫兒正在看台看著她參加U20田徑錦標賽。」<br />\n<br />\n不過，質疑的人都未能提出證據，證明基比斯希爾虛報年齡。一些網民更為基比斯希爾仗義執言，批評胡斯爾路斯不尊重他人。一名網民說：「這是無禮言論，國際田聯應禁制你參賽。」<br />\n<br />\n傳媒正向國際田聯和埃塞俄比亞田徑當局提出查詢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180714/large/1531523105_b5cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180714%2Flarge%2F1531523105_b5cf.jpg&h=f83f7b29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180714/large/1531526632_2bc5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180714%2Flarge%2F1531526632_2bc5.jpg&h=e0aa3e96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180714/58440590\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180714%2F58440590&d=FuZqpavwIwMnS5STjGgweTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=8fdd8d83\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180714%2F58440590&h=467643d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180714/58440590</a>"},{"pid":"0ceef6be16c046fdba6a2d8d609438320089e2c8","tid":742364,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:16:31.000Z","msg":"佢係16歲 咁我仲係胚胎"},{"pid":"14d6693b75278b0ddfb01ddf716c4bb2a2ec8712","tid":742364,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:18:09.000Z","msg":"96下話"},{"pid":"47135b83019a211c9f591de6ded7722b8a286b90","tid":742364,"uid":63864,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:22:19.000Z","msg":"16歲咁老？ 12歲我就信"},{"pid":"a8d3f1169f5d71bb27e77a4fe37be99541381b4e","tid":742364,"uid":179547,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:22:36.000Z","msg":"其實咁大年紀跑得贏班後生仔好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c8fa7ad4946777839f1a038ccfd04c5df0da19b","tid":742364,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T05:12:22.000Z","msg":"係咪勞動過多？個樣又老又殘。"},{"pid":"ccfafe55f15d2650060ef22ff9ec82543f06d9e2","tid":742364,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T07:29:36.000Z","msg":"女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd13cb111dff090002b00800cd08a8ecfbc78551","tid":742364,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T07:53:37.000Z","msg":"肯定係處女"}]}